# Environment Configuration for Advanced Features

This file documents all environment variables required for the advanced features implementation.

## Database Configuration

```bash
# PostgreSQL Connection String (Required)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/event_tracker

# Test Database (Optional - for running test suites)
TEST_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/event_tracker_test
```

## Feature Flags

Enable/disable individual features:

```bash
# Recommendation Engine
FEATURE_AI_RECOMMENDATIONS=true
RECOMMENDATIONS_MAX_RESULTS=5
RECOMMENDATIONS_CACHE_TTL=3600

# Team Formation System
FEATURE_TEAMS=true
TEAMS_MAX_MEMBERS=10
TEAMS_DEFAULT_MAX=5

# Calendar Conflict Detection
FEATURE_CONFLICT_DETECTION=true
CONFLICT_CHECK_INTERVAL=86400  # seconds (1 day)

# Success Probability Scoring
FEATURE_SUCCESS_SCORING=true
SCORING_UPDATE_FREQUENCY=604800  # seconds (1 week)

# Public Profile / Portfolio
FEATURE_PUBLIC_PROFILE=true
PUBLIC_PROFILE_DEFAULT_VISIBILITY=private  # 'public', 'private', 'unlisted'
```

## AI & Recommendation Settings

```bash
# LLM Integration (if using AI for recommendations)
LLM_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
LLM_MODEL=gpt-4
LLM_MAX_TOKENS=500

# Recommendation Algorithm Parameters
REC_SKILL_WEIGHT=0.35         # Weight for skill matching (0-1)
REC_EXPERIENCE_WEIGHT=0.25    # Weight for experience level match
REC_INTEREST_WEIGHT=0.20      # Weight for interest alignment
REC_HISTORY_WEIGHT=0.20       # Weight for application history
```

## Notification Settings

```bash
# Email Notifications
EMAIL_SERVICE=sendgrid  # or 'mailgun', 'ses'
EMAIL_API_KEY=your_key_here
EMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=noreply@eventtracker.com

# Conflict Alerts
SEND_CONFLICT_ALERTS=true
CONFLICT_ALERT_TEMPLATE=conflict_detected

# Recommendation Digest
SEND_RECOMMENDATION_DIGEST=true
DIGEST_FREQUENCY=weekly  # daily, weekly, monthly

# Team Notifications
SEND_TEAM_NOTIFICATIONS=true
```

## Cache Configuration (Optional)

For production, enable caching:

```bash
# Redis Configuration
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
REDIS_DB=0
REDIS_TTL=3600

# Enable Caching
CACHE_RECOMMENDATIONS=true
CACHE_SCORES=true
CACHE_CONFLICTS=true
```

## Database Performance

```bash
# Connection Pool Settings
DB_POOL_MAX=20
DB_POOL_MIN=5
DB_POOL_IDLE_TIMEOUT=30000  # milliseconds

# Query Timeout
DB_QUERY_TIMEOUT=30000  # milliseconds

# Connection Timeout
DB_CONNECTION_TIMEOUT=2000  # milliseconds
```

## Analytics & Monitoring

```bash
# Application Performance Monitoring
APM_ENABLED=true
APM_SERVICE=datadog  # or 'newrelic', 'elastic'
APM_API_KEY=your_key_here

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=info  # debug, info, warn, error
LOG_FORMAT=json  # json or text

# Error Tracking
ERROR_TRACKING_ENABLED=true
ERROR_TRACKING_SERVICE=sentry
SENTRY_DSN=your_sentry_dsn_here
```

## Testing Configuration

```bash
# Jest/Vitest
TEST_ENVIRONMENT=node
TEST_TIMEOUT=10000

# Test Database
TEST_DB_HOST=localhost
TEST_DB_PORT=5432
TEST_DB_NAME=event_tracker_test
TEST_DB_USER=test_user
TEST_DB_PASSWORD=test_password

# Test Seed Data
SEED_TEST_DATA=true
```

## API Configuration

```bash
# API Server
API_HOST=localhost
API_PORT=3000
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# CORS Configuration
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=900000  # 15 minutes in milliseconds
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# Request Size Limits
MAX_REQUEST_SIZE=10mb
MAX_JSON_SIZE=10mb
```

## Authentication

```bash
# JWT/Session Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_here
JWT_EXPIRY=86400  # seconds (24 hours)
SESSION_SECRET=your_session_secret_here
SESSION_TIMEOUT=86400  # seconds

# OAuth (if using external auth)
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_secret
MANUS_CLIENT_ID=your_manus_client_id
MANUS_CLIENT_SECRET=your_manus_secret
```

## File Storage

```bash
# S3 Configuration (for profile image uploads, etc.)
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret_key
S3_BUCKET_NAME=event-tracker-uploads

# File Upload Limits
MAX_FILE_SIZE=5242880  # 5MB in bytes
ALLOWED_FILE_TYPES=jpg,jpeg,png,gif,pdf

# CDN URL (optional)
CDN_URL=https://cdn.yourdomain.com
```

## Email Templates

```bash
# Email Template Paths (if using custom templates)
EMAIL_TEMPLATES_DIR=./templates/email
CONFLICT_ALERT_TEMPLATE=conflict-alert.html
RECOMMENDATION_TEMPLATE=recommendation.html
TEAM_INVITATION_TEMPLATE=team-invitation.html
```

## Feature-Specific Settings

### Recommendation Engine

```bash
# Scoring Algorithm
REC_MIN_SKILL_MATCH=0.3        # Minimum skill match percentage
REC_ACCEPT_THRESHOLD=60        # Minimum score to recommend

# Caching
REC_CACHE_DURATION=3600        # Cache recommendations for 1 hour
REC_UPDATE_FREQUENCY=604800    # Update user profile weekly
```

### Team System

```bash
# Team Defaults
TEAMS_DEFAULT_MAX_MEMBERS=5
TEAMS_MIN_MEMBERS=2
TEAMS_MAX_TOTAL=50             # Max teams user can join

# Team Roles
TEAM_ROLES=lead,member,mentor

# Permissions
ALLOW_TEAM_CREATION=true
ALLOW_TEAM_DELETION=true
TEAM_DELETION_REQUIRES_EMPTY=true
```

### Conflict Detection

```bash
# Conflict Rules
CONFLICT_CHECK_SAME_DAY=true   # Detect same deadline date
CONFLICT_CHECK_DATE_RANGE=false # Detect overlapping date ranges

# Conflict Notification
CONFLICT_URGENCY_THRESHOLD=7   # Days until deadline
CONFLICT_ALERT_RECIPIENTS=user,admin

# Conflict Resolution
AUTO_RESOLVE_CONFLICTS=false   # Auto-resolve if user doesn't act
AUTO_RESOLVE_AFTER_DAYS=14     # Days before auto-resolve
```

### Success Scoring

```bash
# Scoring Parameters
SCORE_EVENT_TYPE_WEIGHT=0.30
SCORE_EXPERIENCE_WEIGHT=0.25
SCORE_ACCEPTANCE_WEIGHT=0.20
SCORE_TIMELINE_WEIGHT=0.15
SCORE_TREND_WEIGHT=0.10

# Score Thresholds
SCORE_HIGH_PROBABILITY=75      # >= 75% considered high
SCORE_MEDIUM_PROBABILITY=50    # 50-75% considered medium
SCORE_LOW_PROBABILITY=25       # < 50% considered low

# Score Update Frequency
SCORE_UPDATE_FREQUENCY=604800  # Weekly updates
SCORE_RECALC_ON_STATUS_CHANGE=true
```

### Public Profile

```bash
# Profile Visibility
DEFAULT_PROFILE_VISIBILITY=private
ALLOW_PUBLIC_PROFILES=true
PROFILE_SHARE_TOKEN_ENABLED=true
PROFILE_SHARE_TOKEN_LENGTH=20

# Profile Display
SHOW_ACCEPTED_APPS=true
SHOW_EXPERIENCE_LEVEL=true
SHOW_SKILLS=true
SHOW_INTERESTS=true

# Privacy
HIDE_EMAIL_PUBLICLY=true
HIDE_PHONE_PUBLICLY=true
HIDE_LOCATION_IF_PRIVATE=true
```

## Deployment Configuration

```bash
# Environment
NODE_ENV=production  # development, staging, production

# Server
PORT=3000
HOSTNAME=0.0.0.0

# SSL/TLS
SSL_CERT_PATH=/etc/ssl/certs/cert.pem
SSL_KEY_PATH=/etc/ssl/private/key.pem
FORCE_HTTPS=true

# Domain
DOMAIN=yourdomain.com
APP_URL=https://yourdomain.com

# Admin Settings
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@yourdomain.com
SUPPORT_EMAIL=support@yourdomain.com
```

## Security

```bash
# Password Hashing
PASSWORD_HASH_ROUNDS=10

# API Keys
API_KEY_ROTATION_PERIOD=2592000  # 30 days

# CSRF Protection
CSRF_ENABLED=true
CSRF_COOKIE_SECURE=true
CSRF_COOKIE_HTTP_ONLY=true

# Security Headers
ENABLE_HELMET=true
ENABLE_HPP=true
```

## Example Development (.env.development)

```bash
NODE_ENV=development
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/event_tracker
TEST_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/event_tracker_test

FEATURE_AI_RECOMMENDATIONS=true
FEATURE_TEAMS=true
FEATURE_CONFLICT_DETECTION=true
FEATURE_SUCCESS_SCORING=true
FEATURE_PUBLIC_PROFILE=true

API_HOST=localhost
API_PORT=3000
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

LOG_LEVEL=debug
```

## Example Production (.env.production)

```bash
NODE_ENV=production
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@prod-db.example.com:5432/event_tracker
REDIS_URL=redis://prod-redis.example.com:6379

FEATURE_AI_RECOMMENDATIONS=true
FEATURE_TEAMS=true
FEATURE_CONFLICT_DETECTION=true
FEATURE_SUCCESS_SCORING=true
FEATURE_PUBLIC_PROFILE=true

API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=3000
DOMAIN=yourdomain.com
FORCE_HTTPS=true

LOG_LEVEL=info
APM_ENABLED=true
APM_SERVICE=datadog
```

## Verification Checklist

Before deploying, verify these environment variables are set:

- [ ] `DATABASE_URL` - PostgreSQL connection string
- [ ] `NODE_ENV` - Set to appropriate environment
- [ ] Feature flags (at least one enabled)
- [ ] `API_HOST` and `API_PORT`
- [ ] `JWT_SECRET` and `SESSION_SECRET`
- [ ] Email service configuration
- [ ] Error tracking service (Sentry DSN)

## Troubleshooting

### "Connection refused" errors
- Verify `DATABASE_URL` is correct
- Check PostgreSQL is running
- Verify network connectivity

### "Permission denied" errors
- Check file permissions for SSL certificates
- Verify S3 credentials have correct permissions
- Check API key validity

### Missing features
- Verify feature flags are set to `true`
- Check that required environment variables are present
- Review logs for initialization errors

### Performance issues
- Increase `DB_POOL_MAX`
- Enable Redis caching
- Check `LOG_LEVEL` is not set to `debug`
- Monitor APM metrics

---

For more information, see the [SETUP_ADVANCED_FEATURES.md](./SETUP_ADVANCED_FEATURES.md) guide.
